text: "Teeth" is a industrial/grunge/rock song by Australian pop rock band 5 Seconds of Summer. It was released on August 21, 2019. It is from their fourth studio album, Calm. It is also on the soundtrack of the third season of the Netflix series 13 Reasons Why.https://twitter.com/5SOS/status/1162413628294926342 At the APRA 2020 Music Awards, "Teeth" was nominated for Song of the Year. It also won Song of the Year at 2020 APRA Music Awards. ==References== Category:2019 songs Category:5 Seconds of Summer songs
